#: app/blueprints/duplicates.py:475
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Hello %(name)s,\n"
"\n"
"During an institutional metadata review at %(institution)s, we identified"
" more than one ORCID iD that may refer to you:\n"
"%(profiles)s\n"
"\n"
"Evidence available for review:\n"
"%(evidence)s\n"
"\n"
"This is an algorithmic candidate, not a confirmation that the records "
"belong to the same person. Please review both ORCID records. If they are "
"yours, contact ORCID Support to request guidance on unifying them. If "
"they belong to different people, please let us know so we can dismiss the"
" match.\n"
"\n"
"The institution cannot merge ORCID records or choose a primary ORCID iD "
"on your behalf."
msgstr ""
"Hola %(name)s:\n"
"\n"
"Durante una revisión institucional de metadatos en %(institution)s, "
"identificamos más de un ORCID iD que podría corresponderte:\n"
"%(profiles)s\n"
"\n"
"Evidencia disponible para revisión:\n"
"%(evidence)s\n"
"\n"
"Este es un candidato algorítmico, no una confirmación de que los "
"registros pertenezcan a la misma persona. Revisa ambos registros ORCID. "
"Si son tuyos, contacta al soporte de ORCID para solicitar orientación "
"sobre cómo unificarlos. Si pertenecen a personas diferentes, avísanos "
"para que podamos descartar la coincidencia.\n"
"\n"
"La institución no puede fusionar registros ORCID ni elegir un ORCID iD "
"principal en tu nombre."

